<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=15723361&amp;query_hl=1&amp;itool=pubmed_docsum" class="external text" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=15723361&amp;query_hl=1&amp;itool=pubmed_docsum" rel="nofollow">Neurofeedback in adolescents and adults with atten...[J Clin Psychol. 2005] - PubMed Result</a></li>
